WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'AlphaQuad' is a game where you try to place a number of letters
in the alphabetical order. When a letter is in the right position
on the board, it will appear in white.

  You play by clicking on the tiles marked by a 'rotation arrow'
icon, located between the letters. Each time you click on one of
these tiles, the letters around it will rotate clockwise by one
position.

  You can choose between 2 game board sizes, a 4 by 4 tiles board
(with the letters from A to P) or a 5 by 5 tiles board (with the
letters from A to Y).

  Have fun!

